    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically robust E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This power unit utilizes individual throttle bodies and a 12.0:1 compression ratio to achieve its 8,400 RPM redline. Power is delivered to the rear wheels via a 7-speed M-DCT dual-clutch transmission and a variable M differential lock, ensuring precise torque distribution. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) for adjustable rebound and compression, while the braking system features cross-drilled rotors for superior heat dissipation. This example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and upgraded throttle actuators, ensuring the valvetrain and bottom end are within tight tolerances. It is a driver-focused machine with a taut suspension geometry and linear power delivery, ready for spirited technical driving.",
      "price": 36800.0,
